import gzip
lines = gzip.open("human_rabbit_genes_combined.gtf.gz", "r").readlines()
lines = lines[5:] # remove header

gene_origin = {}
for line in lines:
    line = line.decode()
    origin = line.split('\t')[0]
    if "Hum" in origin:
        origin = "Hum"
    elif "Rab" in origin:
        origin = "Rab"
    else:
        print("Unknown origin error!")
    gene_origin["ENS"+line.split("ENS")[1].split('"')[0]] = origin

count_table_dict = {}
keys = ["P13104_9002_S2_L001", "P13104_9002_S2_L002", 
        "P13104_9003_S3_Retransferred", "P13104_9003_S3_L002",
        "P15064_Experiment_Repeat"]
for file, key in zip(files, keys):
    print(key)
    mat = mmread(file+"matrix.mtx.gz").todense()
    matbarcodes = np.array(pd.read_csv(file+"barcodes.tsv.gz", sep='\t', header=None)[0])
    matgenes = np.array(pd.read_csv(file+"features.tsv.gz", sep='\t', header=None)[0])
    matdf = pd.DataFrame(mat)
    matdf.index = matgenes
    matdf.columns = matbarcodes
    matdf['Species'] = [gene_origin[i] for i in matdf.index]
    count_table_dict[key] = copy.deepcopy(matdf)

r_pcts = {}

    df = count_table_dict[key]
    r = df.groupby('Species').sum().reset_index().set_index("Species")
    r_pct = (r/r.sum(0)).T
    r_pct = r_pct.sort_values(by="Hum", ascending=False)
    print(key,"=>",(sum(r_pct["Hum"] > r_pct["Rab"])/len(r_pct))*100, "percent human cells,",sum(r_pct["Hum"] > r_pct["Rab"]))
    r_pcts[key] = r_pct

    adata[:, mito_genes].X, axis=1) / np.sum(adata.X, axis=1)
# add the total counts per cell as observations-annotation to adata
adata.obs['n_counts'] = adata.X.sum(axis=1)

from sklearn.svm import SVR

def filter_cv_vs_mean(S: np.ndarray, N: int, svr_gamma: float=None, plot: bool=True, min_expr_cells: int=2,
                      max_expr_avg: float=20, min_expr_avg: float=0) -> np.ndarray:
    muS = S.mean(1)
    detected_bool = ((S > 0).sum(1) > min_expr_cells) & (muS < max_expr_avg) & (muS > min_expr_avg)
    
    Sf = S[detected_bool, :]
    mu = Sf.mean(1)
    sigma = Sf.std(1, ddof=1)

    cv = sigma / mu
    log_m = np.log2(mu)
    log_cv = np.log2(cv)
    
    if svr_gamma is None:
        svr_gamma = 150. / len(mu)
    
    svr = SVR(gamma=svr_gamma)
    svr.fit(log_m[:, None], log_cv)
    fitted_fun = svr.predict
    ff = fitted_fun(log_m[:, None])
    score = log_cv - ff

    xnew = np.linspace(np.min(log_m), np.max(log_m))
    ynew = svr.predict(xnew[:, None])

    nth_score = np.sort(score)[::-1][N]
    
    if plot:
        plt.scatter(log_m[score > nth_score], log_cv[score > nth_score], s=3, alpha=0.4, c="tab:red")
        plt.scatter(log_m[score <= nth_score], log_cv[score <= nth_score], s=3, alpha=0.4, c="tab:blue")
        mu_linspace = np.linspace(np.min(log_m), np.max(log_m))
        plt.plot(mu_linspace, fitted_fun(mu_linspace[:, None]), c="k")
        plt.xlabel("log2 mean S")
        plt.ylabel("log2 CV S")
    
    cv_mean_score = np.zeros(detected_bool.shape)
    cv_mean_score[~detected_bool] = np.min(score) - 1e-16
    cv_mean_score[detected_bool] = score
    cv_mean_selected = cv_mean_score >= nth_score
    return cv_mean_selected
